import PropTypes from "prop-types"

const TaskModel = {
    slug: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
    taskName: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
    taskCreationData:/*  PropTypes.instanceOf(Date).isRequired || */ PropTypes.number.isRequired,
    taskDescription: PropTypes.string.isRequired ,
    taskAssignedBy: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
    taskObservations: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
    taskLastUpdate: /* PropTypes.instanceOf(Date).isRequired || */ PropTypes.number.isRequired,
    taskCliente: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
    taskType: PropTypes.oneOf(["llamada","visita"]),
    taskDone: PropTypes.bool.isRequired
}

export default TaskModel
